{
  "title": "Peppery Malaysian Rice Noodles",
  "description": "A kid-friendly, rich and juicy dish with a Malaysian twist, perfect for a weeknight dinner. This lacto-vegetarian-friendly recipe is made with red pepper paste and cooked to perfection with pressure-cooking.",
