  "instructions": [
    "Heat 2 tablespoons of vegetable oil in a large pressure cooker over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion, garlic, and ginger, and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the red pepper paste and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the coconut milk, water, soy sauce, sugar, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the rice noodles and stir to coat with the sauce.",
    "Close the pressure cooker and cook at 10 pounds of pressure for 5 minutes.",
    "Quick-release the pressure, then open the cooker and stir in the chopped green onions.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with additional green onions if desired."
